<p>I am Redel. I am 37 years old and i have one daughter. My first experience to work as a domestic helper was in Dubai, i worked with one employer fo 4 years and 2 months. When i came they have only 1 daughter she was 4 months old. Then 2 new kids were born. I was taking care of the 3 kids. My everyday routine are cleaning the house, ironing, washing the clothes, washing the car and assist to my madaam when shes cooking. i have also experience as a nanny of twins in philippine for only 3 months because then i started to work here in hong kong as a domestic helper. In my current employer, she have 2 kids and when i came here the eldest is 3 years old and now his going to 7 years old and while the youngest is when i came here his 7 months old and his going to 5 years old. My every day routines here are preparing things to go to school, bring the youngest and pick from school, and buy food for dinner ang groceries, cleaning the house, I am hardworking, honest and respectful.</p>
